# `patchpilot-k3s` is off-limits

The directory / repo copy **`patchpilot-k3s`** is a parallel tree the operator maintains themselves.

- **Do not** change, create, delete, or refactor files under **`patchpilot-k3s`** unless the operator **explicitly** asks to work there in that conversation.
- **Do** restrict codebase edits to **`patchpilot`** (this project) by default.

If the operator wants the same change in both places, they will sync **`patchpilot-k3s`** on their own unless they clearly request edits in **`patchpilot-k3s`**.
